Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.74,0:00:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,☆Dragon Ball Super☆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.61,0:00:14.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,曾经淡忘的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.84,0:00:19.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如今再续前缘　又开始燃亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.52,0:00:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给星星都连上线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.85,0:00:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就这样给宇宙画出了门框
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.44,0:00:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跻身于全新的舞台上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.45,0:00:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,向诸神发出挑战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.62,0:00:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强烈☆猛烈☆活力满泻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.66,0:00:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's Go！Go！恐慌奔走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.17,0:00:49.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你输了就能变更强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.88,0:00:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知天高地厚又何妨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.55,0:01:00.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,生无可悔　身无界限　一往无前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.51,0:01:02.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,壮烈☆激烈☆活力爆裂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.64,0:01:05.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's Go！Yes！拳脚不绝！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.14,0:01:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去沐浴颤抖的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.90,0:01:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一个壮大传说　正在等着你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.47,0:01:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第6宇宙和第7宇宙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.09,0:01:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,格斗比赛终于开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.82,0:01:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比赛结束！出界！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.37,0:01:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第7宇宙的孙悟空选手获胜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.76,0:01:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟空漂亮地拿下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.71,0:01:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,首场比赛的胜利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.13,0:02:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,永远不要放弃，要振作起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.47,0:02:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是我鼓励孩子们时说过的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.85,0:02:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要对说过的话负责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.66,0:02:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有破绽！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.04,0:02:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但受到下一个对手弗罗斯特的一击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.55,0:02:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跌落到场外，令全场大为震惊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.59,0:02:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,破坏神选拔格斗比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.39,0:02:51.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下来会如何发展？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.94,0:03:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「比克VS弗罗斯特 孤注一掷的魔贯光杀炮！」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.98,0:03:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,分出胜负了！出界！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.11,0:03:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第6宇宙的弗罗斯特选手获胜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.20,0:03:47.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成功了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.49,0:03:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀，悟空输了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.20,0:03:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,卡卡罗特竟然输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.75,0:03:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太轻视对手的攻击了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.83,0:03:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定是大脑受到损伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.42,0:04:01.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一瞬间失去意识了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.67,0:04:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么搞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.38,0:04:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个笨蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.96,0:04:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,克林！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.84,0:04:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,诶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.67,0:04:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都是因为你说「不知道该为谁加油」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.30,0:04:12.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,孙君才会输掉比赛的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.81,0:04:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,诶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.02,0:04:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,布玛小姐你不是也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.93,0:04:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟…悟…悟空！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.44,0:04:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妈妈！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.98,0:04:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟空，振作一点！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.32,0:04:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟空！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.33,0:04:33.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟空！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.20,0:04:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎，哎呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.29,0:04:42.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么回事，我输了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.67,0:04:44.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,悟空！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.46,0:04:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我还担心你会不会死了呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.42,0:04:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别这样，大家都看着呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.64,0:04:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你没事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.98,0:04:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真行啊你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.31,0:04:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,诶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.73,0:05:01.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我都没看清是什么招式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.23,0:05:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,连我自己也不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.77,0:05:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为我当时也拼命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.69,0:05:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但我很清楚一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.49,0:05:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你把我的极限提升到了新的高度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.87,0:05:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.75,0:05:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然很艰苦，但跟你比赛很开心，谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.21,0:05:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是败给你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.60,0:05:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好棒啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.02,0:05:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,精彩的比赛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.99,0:05:52.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢你们带来的感动！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.28,0:05:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两个人都很帅啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.91,0:06:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是厉害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.62,0:06:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果银河巡逻队有这样的高手就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.80,0:06:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的比赛已经结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.76,0:06:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在这里安心地看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.31,0:06:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀，还真是丢人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.10,0:06:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是丢人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.35,0:06:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你以为这么说我就会原谅你吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.56,0:06:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你如果全力以赴的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.65,0:06:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该能轻松获胜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.40,0:06:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,话…话是这么说啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.90,0:06:33.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我以为变成超级赛亚人就能赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.24,0:06:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,结果却输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.11,0:06:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没办法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.95,0:06:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下次我绝对不会输的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.20,0:06:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下次？这场比赛才是最重要的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.71,0:06:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果这次比赛输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.42,0:06:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以后象帕这混蛋会一直…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.75,0:06:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂！比鲁斯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.63,0:06:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你该不会是生气了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.01,0:06:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,生气了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.43,0:07:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…我才没有生气呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.64,0:07:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这家伙该不会是你的王牌吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.27,0:07:07.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你着急了吧？着急了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.57,0:07:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比鲁斯大人，要忍住，忍住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.41,0:07:21.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你堂堂正正全力以赴地比赛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.74,0:07:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,胜负根本就不重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.71,0:07:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打了一场精彩的比赛啊，悟空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.84,0:07:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下来，下一位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.30,0:07:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和弗罗斯特对战的第7宇宙的选手是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.55,0:07:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比克选手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.60,0:07:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你觉得我有机会赢吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.44,0:07:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.77,0:07:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你这混蛋，说得这么直接
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.86,0:07:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我干脆弃权吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.61,0:07:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不，为了下一个出战的贝吉塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.78,0:08:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你尽量去消耗一下弗罗斯特的体力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.66,0:08:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对后面的战斗有好处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.04,0:08:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的作用就是这个啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.84,0:08:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你打算用最终形态跟我打吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.97,0:08:17.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,稍微放放水怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.97,0:08:20.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.01,0:08:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已经没力气杀你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.47,0:08:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即便如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.64,0:08:27.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我可没打算输给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.89,0:08:31.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们这些家伙，都小看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.12,0:08:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请…请各位稍等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.08,0:08:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,卡卡罗特不可能因为受到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.08,0:08:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那种程度的攻击失去意识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.67,0:08:57.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总感觉另有隐情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.52,0:09:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,干嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.22,0:09:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.14,0:09:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为这里看得更清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.82,0:09:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比赛开始！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.11,0:09:21.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的招式全都让你们看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.32,0:09:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剩下的也只有冲劲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.70,0:09:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但我会化冲劲为武器和你战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.13,0:09:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个架势，是魔贯光杀炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.09,0:09:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真厉害啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.63,0:09:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在我看来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.30,0:09:43.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那只是有弱点的雕虫小技啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.39,0:09:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,诶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.10,0:09:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来你打算直接放大招啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.73,0:09:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且这个大招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.94,0:09:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,貌似需要聚集相当多的气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.44,0:09:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.03,0:10:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被看穿很正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.37,0:10:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很好！保持这个势头！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.72,0:10:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很久没看到了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.47,0:10:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这不是用雕虫小技就能战胜的对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.01,0:10:29.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那种伎俩！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.29,0:10:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是何等强大的注意力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.20,0:10:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但你已经受了伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.96,0:10:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可能再四处闪躲了吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.88,0:11:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,分身？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.55,0:11:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个家伙从刚才开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.93,0:11:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就只是不停地躲来躲去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.31,0:11:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,裁判，赶紧给他黄牌！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.10,0:11:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,警告他一下！干脆判他失去资格！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.94,0:11:17.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是他的战术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.81,0:11:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,并不算犯规
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.77,0:11:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你只是一个小小的裁判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.03,0:11:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想和破坏神作对吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.53,0:11:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,闭嘴！在比赛中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.99,0:11:29.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,裁判比神更有权威！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.66,0:11:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,您真的这么认为吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.54,0:11:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.17,0:11:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已经够了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.42,0:11:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以反击了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.21,0:11:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不，他还想继续聚气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.34,0:11:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他准备用超越极限的一击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.80,0:11:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,决出胜负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.47,0:11:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被他这样拖时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.31,0:11:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且因为光根本看不见他的脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.52,0:11:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有些不爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.53,0:12:12.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那样就无法发招了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.75,0:12:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟他保持距离，比克！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.97,0:12:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.43,0:12:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我赢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.93,0:12:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.85,0:12:40.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.61,0:12:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你上当了，弗罗斯特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.94,0:12:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在考虑如何聚气的同时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.24,0:12:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还在考虑一件事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.20,0:12:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是如何击中你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.80,0:13:21.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的注意力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.26,0:13:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都只集中到你逐渐提高的气上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.35,0:13:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以把你的气息打散的一瞬间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.73,0:13:27.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我坚信我已经赢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.56,0:13:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,于是你出现了破绽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.10,0:13:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,难道说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.61,0:13:33.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的腿故意被我打穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.32,0:13:35.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也是为了创造这个局面？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.28,0:13:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被摆了一道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.24,0:13:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这可真是你的绝招啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.07,0:13:43.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,确实，这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.28,0:13:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你必杀的一击就不会打偏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.00,0:13:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你别看我这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.37,0:13:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在第7宇宙我可是公认的智囊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.79,0:13:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知道我的战斗方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.80,0:13:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是你输给我的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.34,0:14:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看招！魔贯光…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.19,0:14:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有破绽！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.31,0:14:14.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.36,0:14:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.20,0:14:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是我中了你这一招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.86,0:14:22.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我肯定就输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.95,0:14:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,非常精彩的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.89,0:14:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的超级坚固的屋顶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.93,0:14:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我会修好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.90,0:15:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,胜者是，弗罗斯特选手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.62,0:15:06.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.91,0:15:08.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.45,0:15:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看不懂，那个家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.42,0:15:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,究竟是用了什么手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.92,0:15:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我有异议！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.17,0:15:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了，加克？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.80,0:15:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他犯规了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.26,0:15:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,诶？怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.34,0:15:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弗罗斯特选手使用了武器！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.60,0:15:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,武器？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.76,0:15:30.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你去检查他的右臂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.39,0:15:32.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那里藏着像针一样的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.81,0:15:34.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这可逃不过我的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.77,0:15:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你干什么！竟敢找茬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.77,0:15:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太不像话了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.23,0:15:40.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊，我曾经在玛尤奈行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.90,0:15:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和弗罗斯特先生一起作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.49,0:15:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他是拼了命从宇宙海盗手里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.24,0:15:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拯救市民的大英雄啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.74,0:15:50.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么会犯规呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.37,0:15:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加克，弗罗斯特不是那样的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.83,0:15:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你真的看见了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.08,0:16:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小看我的好视力可是会吃亏的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.46,0:16:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,裁判，检查他的身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.26,0:16:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比赛输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.76,0:16:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就找这种无聊的借口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.60,0:16:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,随便查吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.81,0:16:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但要是什么都没有我就把你破坏掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.56,0:16:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,诶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.52,0:16:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那…那算了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.81,0:16:19.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不，给我好好检查一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.27,0:16:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算你被破坏掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.23,0:16:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟我没什么关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.03,0:16:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟我也没什么关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.49,0:16:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,裁判，赶快检查！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.98,0:16:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好晕啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.11,0:17:04.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎…怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.82,0:17:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这不是武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.41,0:17:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而是我身体的一部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.03,0:17:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不…不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.74,0:17:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很明显有加工的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.00,0:17:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弗罗斯特选手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.37,0:17:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由于犯规失去资格！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.96,0:17:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,胜者是比克选手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.63,0:17:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你真能干啊加克！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.39,0:17:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第一次觉得你挺帅的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.97,0:17:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不会吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.85,0:17:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.93,0:17:36.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,您这样的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.43,0:17:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么要做这种卑鄙的事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.69,0:17:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.48,0:17:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是弗罗斯特的本性啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.19,0:17:47.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,袭击玛尤奈行星的宇宙海盗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.49,0:17:50.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是他率领的秘密组织啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.36,0:17:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.78,0:17:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,诶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.83,0:17:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你这么说也太过分了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.58,0:17:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,芭朵斯小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.63,0:18:06.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自己挑起战争并平息战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.71,0:18:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,廉价收购因战火而荒废的土地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.76,0:18:15.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后通过二次开发和重建的特权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.26,0:18:16.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大赚一笔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.52,0:18:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是我发明的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.14,0:18:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,商业模式喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.73,0:18:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么啊，他干的这些勾当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.86,0:18:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和弗利萨差不多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.28,0:18:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了掩饰他的犯规
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.82,0:18:34.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这家伙把好人演得很彻底啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.49,0:18:37.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使是在别的宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.54,0:18:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弗利萨也不可能是好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.59,0:18:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来耍计谋的并不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.51,0:18:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而是你这混蛋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.43,0:18:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知道我的战斗方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.35,0:19:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是你输给我的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.98,0:19:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,智囊先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.48,0:19:04.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.94,0:19:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你为什么选那家伙？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.65,0:19:09.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为你并没有命令我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.61,0:19:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把选手们的品行纳入考虑范围之内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.03,0:19:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对我说「太麻烦了，
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.53,0:19:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你找几个一定能赢的家伙来」的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.87,0:19:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是您喔，象帕大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.08,0:19:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下一场比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.50,0:19:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,给我好好加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.00,0:19:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你让我丢这么大的脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.72,0:19:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要把你破坏掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.22,0:19:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.89,0:19:38.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不需要破坏他，也不需要判他出局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.56,0:19:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下一个轮到我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.81,0:19:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要亲手打倒这个混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.73,0:19:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是，比克选手的败北
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.06,0:19:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已经被取消了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.61,0:19:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以下一场比赛还是他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.44,0:19:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比克说他要弃权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.25,0:20:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.33,0:20:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.42,0:20:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不把他破坏掉，我的气消不下来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.96,0:20:11.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们别自作主张！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.63,0:20:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这不是挺好的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.51,0:20:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拿回了参赛资格，对方选手弃权了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.05,0:20:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是我方的胜利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.14,0:20:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对我方没有任何损失啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.93,0:20:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,话是这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.81,0:20:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,您想输给比鲁斯大人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.52,0:20:31.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弗罗斯特！如果你赢了下一场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.57,0:20:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你让我丢人这件事就一笔勾销
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.15,0:20:37.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再下一场比赛如果你还能打赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.15,0:20:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就考虑出资援助的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.12,0:20:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你能赢吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.71,0:20:46.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.12,0:20:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是藐视一切的笑声啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.17,0:20:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和比鲁斯大人一样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.88,0:20:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂！贝吉塔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.30,0:20:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好好地收拾他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.92,0:20:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让我痛快痛快！明白了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.31,0:21:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜托了喔！贝吉塔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.40,0:21:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说算我赢也没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.23,0:21:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来还真是有自信呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.45,0:21:20.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到时候可别后悔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.45,0:21:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的声音，听了真不爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.37,0:21:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.73,0:21:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,永别了亲爱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.52,0:21:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,淡红的天空下的我和你　我站在你右边　而你待在我的左边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.62,0:22:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「我很喜欢你　这一生都不会忘记你」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.12,0:22:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想说出口　又咽了回去　不如还是　把话埋在心底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.50,0:22:11.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,突然两人被困在　一场滂沱落花雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.71,0:22:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,簌簌的　谱成一首动人旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.80,0:22:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,至少把你的身影　从我的眼前隐去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.18,0:22:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渐染一片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.85,0:22:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,淡红色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.06,0:22:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,的情绪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.44,0:22:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渐染一片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.23,0:22:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,永别时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.32,0:22:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.32,0:22:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗨！我是悟空！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.19,0:22:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么回事啊，那个弗罗斯特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.03,0:22:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来是个大坏蛋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.70,0:22:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我完全被他骗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.41,0:22:47.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过贝吉塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.75,0:22:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来你和我不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.71,0:22:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根本不给他使用犯规招式的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.33,0:22:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尽全力狠狠地揍他吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.21,0:22:57.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下集 『龙珠超』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.30,0:23:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「化愤怒为力量吧！贝吉塔的全力战斗」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.38,0:23:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定要看啊

